        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "p",
        "class": "",
        "text": "Zechariah the son of Jehoiada the priest.—“The priest,” i.e., the high priest, is an epithet of Jehoiada, not of Zechariah.",
        "children": [
          {
            "element": "span",
            "class": "bld",
            "text": "Zechariah the son of Jehoiada the priest.",
            "children": []
          },
          {
            "element": "span",
            "class": "",
            "text": "—“The priest,” ",
            "children": []
          },
          {
            "element": "span",
            "class": "ital",
            "text": "i.e.,",
            "children": []
          },
          {
            "element": "span",
            "class": "",
            "text": " the high priest, is an epithet of Jehoiada, not of Zechariah.",
            "children": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "element": "p",
        "class": "",
        "text": "Which stood above the people.—Probably on the steps of the inner court of the Temple, facing the people who were assembled in the outer court.",
        "children": [
          {
            "element": "span",
            "class": "bld",
            "text": "Which stood above the people.",
            "children": []
          },
          {
            "element": "span",
            "class": "",
            "text": "—Probably on the steps of the inner court of the Temple, facing the people who were assembled in the outer court.",
            "children": []
          }
